sequenceDiagram
    participant C as MCP Client
    participant S as MCP Server

    rect rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.12)
    note over C,S: Stage 1 — Initialization (Handshake)
    C->>S: initialize (protocol version, client capabilities)
    S-->>C: initialize response (server capabilities, negotiated version)
    C-)S: initialized (notification — no ID, no response)
    end

    rect rgba(240, 249, 255, 0.6)
    note over C,S: Stage 2 — Normal Operation
    C->>S: tools/list
    S-->>C: [search_missions, get_weather, ...]
    C->>S: tools/call ("search_missions", args)
    S-->>C: { result: [...] }
    C->>S: resources/read ("crew://schedule")
    S-->>C: { content: "..." }
    S-)C: notifications/progress (60/100)
    end

    rect rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.08)
    note over C,S: Stage 3 — Shutdown
    C-)S: disconnect / close transport
    note right of S: Server frees resources
    end
